@NODE RM_PLAY "Player's Guide"

  * Most importantly, don't be near a wall when you are shot. If you have
    nowhere to move you take the full force of whatever weapon hits you.
    This is usually devastating.

  * Learn what the power-ups are. The difference between good and bad
    weapons is the difference between winning and losing.

  * Avoid thin tunnels and dead ends as you can easily be pinned down by
    most weapons.

  * Only use highly explosive weapons in open space.

  * Don't be too close to a wall when firing. Certain things can detonate
    in your face.

  * Watch your back. A common tactic is for a third player to sneak up
    on two people fighting and kill them both when their energy is low.

    That's about it. The rest you can learn for yourself. Everyone has
  slightly different tactics when they play so try to learn your what
  your opponents are likely to do. Oh and be sure and have fun.

@ENDNODE

